            <span class="text-2xl">üß±</span>
            Languages & Frameworks
          </h2>
          <ul class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed space-y-2">
            <li><strong class="text-white">PHP / Laravel</strong> ‚Äî Primary back-end stack</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">JavaScript / TypeScript</strong> ‚Äî Front-end and full-stack</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">React / Next.js</strong> ‚Äî Interactive UIs and SSR apps</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Astro</strong> ‚Äî Static site generation (this portfolio)</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Tailwind CSS</strong> ‚Äî Utility-first styling</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">WordPress</strong> ‚Äî CMS development and custom themes</li>
          </ul>
        </article>

        <!-- DevOps & Infrastructure -->
        <article class="uses-section">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-neon-yellow mb-3 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-2xl">‚òÅÔ∏è</span>
            DevOps & Infrastructure
          </h2>
          <ul class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed space-y-2">
            <li><strong class="text-white">Docker</strong> ‚Äî Containerized development environments</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">AWS</strong> ‚Äî EC2, S3, CloudFront, Route 53</li>
            <li><strong class="text-white">Jenkins</strong> ‚Äî CI/CD pipelines</li>
